name: Nahuelito
description:
/From the depths of Lake Nahuel Huapi, el Nahuelito watched us play in the water. Always from the darkness, without anyone being able to see him, but always knowing he was there./

The Nahuelito was born in the city of Bariloche, Patagonia, Argentina and is found in Lake Nahuel Huapi. In the depths of the icy waters, where the most mysterious creatures dwell.
Some say it is a relative of the Loch Ness Monster but we have not yet been able to prove it.
